ing: 1 (1.5 fluid ounce) jigger fruit-flavored rum liqueur
4 fluid ounces lemon-lime flavored carbonated beverage
des: "This is a drink that a friend and I made up one night while I was tending bar at a local private club."
ins: Fill a tall glass with ice. Pour in rum liqueur and vodka. Fill with lemon-lime soda.
